nce in the construction industry we are certified energy plan examiners certified energy analysts certified green building professionals certified greenpoint raters certified home energy rating system raters hers raters and certified calgreen special inspectors we can even help with the preparation and submission of required documentation for california title  energy conservation and green building submissions we are passionate about green energy solutions and we know the business inside and out   at rick’s energy solutions we assist homeowners in making their living spaces more energy efficient and ecofriendly it all begins by understanding the home as a comprehensive system and understanding how well your household performs through a home energy audit this involves evaluating your home for its green building environmental impacts and its carbon footprint most houses do not operate to their fullest energy potential even if the houses are newly constructed many homes leak air conditioning during the summer and heat during the winter due to faulty vent installation windows with poor retention and myriad other reasons   finding issues and improving efficiency   a lot of lighting and appliances utilize more energy than needed to function this is incredibly wasteful but very difficult to detect many air ducts leak which wastes heated and cooled air in addition many water fixtures are wasteful using more water than necessary for typical applications these are all aspects our hers raters look for in your home during our audit we identify hidden issues and offer solutions to help your home consume less energy and resources without requiring you to make any lifestyle changes these solutions include duct redesign air sealing lighting and appliance upgrades window upgrade faucet and water fixture replacement and more all energy problems in your home can be met by our efficient energy solutions   our services are very important when it comes to architects designers and contractors these people are responsible for the construction of future homes and commercial buildings and renovations of existing structures when we work with them in helping to shape their next projects you can rest assured that we are setting a new energysmart status quo for buildings to come   one team providing smart energy solutions   it is very much a team effort when working with architects it is our job to prepare the documentation required for obtaining the energy star rating on new homes the architects are the ones who bring the ecofriendly visions to life we also prepare the documentation required to submit to the irs for tax rebates for energy conservation measures at rick’s energy solutions we make sure that designers contractors and architects are up to par with the best knowledge techniques and technologies when it comes to energy efficiency it is our way of nipping energy problems in the bud we consult on such projects as home additions remodeling jobs and the construction of entirely new homes and commercial buildings to ensure the highest quality of environmental friendliness   when it comes to energy solutions in santa rosa california and the surrounding areas including sonoma mendocino lake marin and napa counties rick’s energy solutions is the most efficient and affordable option we have more than 0 years of experience in the construction industry with  of those years working in building inspection and plans examination our team is equipped to handle any project from all angles imaginable we have our finger on the pulse of what is needed in terms of the most uptodate energyefficient conservation techniques and know the logistics that are involved with making everything come together effectively   we also work closely with architects contractors and homeowners we could not do what we do without their skills and cooperation there is no other green building consultant or energy conservation construction company that has all of their bases covered the way we do the best defense is a good offense   get started on becoming more energy efficient today   rick’s energy solutions is privileged to be doing such important work that affects both our futures and yours alike if you are a homeowner a home designer an architect or a contractor we would love nothing more than to give you an evaluation of your home or planned project our consultation service can help you identify improvements that can be made at your home to help protect the environment and even shape the future of how buildings are constructed   we offer both home and commercial energy audits and are certified by the california association of building energy consultants cabec build it green efficiency first the international code council icc and calcerts we could not be prouder of our company’s past successes and we are laser focused on the horizon of energy conservation   as energy conservation and green building consultants we’re standing by to assist homeowners contractors and designers alike in identifying home energy solutions preparing and submitting california title  energy conservation and green building compliance documents recommending small changes to improve efficiency and much more contact us today by calling 5 and lets work to create a better more energyefficient tomorrow         contact us name email phonemessagewould you like to receive emails from us in the futureyesnocommentsthis field is for validation purposes and should be left unchanged home owners our green building consulting auditing  home performance testing services will have your home running at peak performance for efficiency lower maintenance and comfort • green energy upgrade survey• energy efficiency audits• energystar for homes• green building consulting• greenpoint rating• hers ratings• home performance testing• title  services• water efficiency audits  buildersarchitects our customers may benefit from the services in one or more of the following waysreduced carbon footprint for 